  - question: "Does Appwrite Auth meet enterprise compliance requirements?"
    answer: "Appwrite is GDPR, HIPAA, and SOC-2 compliant, with built-in encryption, password hashing, common-password protection, and session limits. These are the same compliance baselines Auth0 offers."
